Program: Omnibus
Title: The Sound of Silence
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376k80
Last Broadcast Date: 09 January 1992
A look at the search for silence as the world gets noisier. Artists and writers express their desire for the absence of sound. Contributors include art critic Waldemar Januszczak. Picture: Woman on beach, Credit: Thinkstock